{"tid":561913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【警已報】台狗破解港人fb密碼，仲擺上網威","createTime":"2018-02-15T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T20:51:13.000Z","uid":17232,"like":104,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"f98f8415970520d4747343c31b36be4629e3d6af","tid":561913,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"原post：台狗破解港人fb密碼，仲擺上網威<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/557061/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/557061/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n更正：自稱Hacker個條友已經證實係香港人，但係佢Youtube上既片全部都係講純正普通話。<br />\n<br />\n呢隻自稱Hacker既崇台狗走去hack人地fb acc，仲要將罪證擺撚埋上Youtube，最後比連登巴打追擊到del埋條片。好彩我有backup擺翻上youtube，點知條友仲咁唔知醜走入黎叫我del左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/194712_3ac85d08d865e1968b3a0a4dc6a3885a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F194712_3ac85d08d865e1968b3a0a4dc6a3885a.png&h=9ef4d42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果當然係比一眾巴打屌撚死，我就要求佢向受害者道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/194910_f83fffcf73c6ee85c3d34d3ebbe12874.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F194910_f83fffcf73c6ee85c3d34d3ebbe12874.PNG&h=ec79f83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係到依家時間已經過左三日，我完全見唔到佢條channel有任何既道歉片，而且條仆街仲檢舉埋我條片，搞到條片del撚埋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/195010_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F195010_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=5b69f85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻要求Youtube撤銷控訴（唔知點解一入呢個頁面就係殘體）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/195241_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F195241_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=0bde5543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便報埋驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/195126_a55ba55217dd16c4ffb58f879422899f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F195126_a55ba55217dd16c4ffb58f879422899f.png&h=dfad9051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後備backup(1)：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uKkhiizxijA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuKkhiizxijA&d=Ex020SWajDlk0bcnFTs8%2FJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5598061c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uKkhiizxijA</a><br />\n<br />\n後備backup(2)：<a href=\"https://saren.wtako.net/%E3%80%90BACKUP%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%B1%81%E5%AD%A9%E7%BE%9E%E8%BE%B1%20%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%A7%AD%E6%8E%89facebook%21%20%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E5%93%AD%E8%91%97%E5%8F%AB%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD-7wIk8qHmPZs.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsaren.wtako.net%2F%25E3%2580%2590BACKUP%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B1%2581%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E7%25BE%259E%25E8%25BE%25B1%2520%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%25A7%25AD%25E6%258E%2589facebook%2521%2520%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%2593%25AD%25E8%2591%2597%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD-7wIk8qHmPZs.mp4&d=Ex020SWajDlk0bcnFTs8%2FJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=02339ac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://saren.wtako.net/%E3%80%90BACKUP%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%B1%81%E5%AD%A9%E7%BE%9E%E8%BE%B1%20%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%A7%AD%E6%8E%89facebook%21%20%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E5%93%AD%E8%91%97%E5%8F%AB%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD-7wIk8qHmPZs.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣巴哈姆特討論link：<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?page=3&amp;bsn=60076&amp;snA=4404956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fpage%3D3%26bsn%3D60076%26snA%3D4404956&d=Ex020SWajDlk0bcnFTs8%2FJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c7f1867c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?page=3&amp;bsn=60076&amp;snA=4404956</a>"},{"pid":"ded1b786120632c753a01e51a5667a958e39f788","tid":561913,"uid":140979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1bd06ea5e06af31c50a111896eb77b347dea7c","tid":561913,"uid":33825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a972c6c3720d3456cfa646f9d5331c564135302","tid":561913,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"你開左3個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f3873ee2f64dc9ae0ab19cbb0adb6872e8250a","tid":561913,"uid":140979,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/200254_78fc285e0e43e5f50ea3ecb8bb625397.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F200254_78fc285e0e43e5f50ea3ecb8bb625397.png&h=a4d7a713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公然Hack鳩人仲可以話係為左提醒大家密碼安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無撚恥到呢。 啲賊偷野係提醒大家店鋪安全啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\